items.title: System Tests Fail Due to Missing Local Dependencies

labels.name: api: cloudasset
labels.description: Issues related to the Cloud Asset Inventory API.

labels.name: type: cleanup
labels.description: An internal cleanup or hygiene concern.

items.body:
This library was originally part of the google-cloud-python repository. The Noxfile has local dependencies such as '../api_core' . These need to be updated to point to their module names, I believe.

Without this, the System tests cannot build using Nox.
